er builds without errors\n226:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n227:   - Verification: `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile -t agentcube-test-workloadmanager . && echo \"PASS\"`\n228: \n229: - [ ] **T6.2**: Build router image successfully\n230:   - Purpose: Verify router builds without errors\n231:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n232:   - Verification: `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.router -t agentcube-test-router . && echo \"PASS\"`\n233: \n234: - [ ] **T6.3**: Build picod image successfully\n235:   - Purpose: Verify picod builds without errors\n236:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n237:   - Verification: `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile.picod -t agentcube-test-picod . && echo \"PASS\"`\n238: \n239: - [ ] **T6.4**: Verify workloadmanager image size <50MB\n240:   - Purpose: Confirm image meets size target\n241:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n242:   - Verification: `docker image inspect agentcube-test-workloadmanager --format='{{.Size}}' | awk '{if($1<50000000) print \"PASS\"; else print \"FAIL\"}'`\n243: \n244: - [ ] **T6.5**: Verify router image size <50MB\n245:   - Purpose: Confirm image meets size target\n246:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n247:   - Verification: `docker image inspect agentcube-test-router --format='{{.Size}}' | awk '{if($1<50000000) print \"PASS\"; else print \"FAIL\"}'`\n248: \n249: - [ ] **T6.6**: Verify picod image size <100MB\n250:   - Purpose: Confirm image meets size target (Ubuntu base larger)\n251:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n252:   - Verification: `docker image inspect agentcube-test-picod --format='{{.Size}}' | awk '{if($1<100000000) print \"PASS\"; else print \"FAIL\"}'`\n253: \n254: ### Phase 7: Runtime Verification Tests (ST-7)\n255: \n256: - [ ] **T7.1**: Verify workloadmanager binary exists in runtime image\n257:   - Purpose: Confirm binary copied from builder\n258:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n259:   - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-workloadmanager test -f /app/bin/workloadmanager`\n260: \n261: - [ ] **T7.2**: Verify router binary exists in runtime image\n262:   - Purpose: Confirm binary copied from builder\n263:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n264:   - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-router test -f /app/bin/router`\n265: \n266: - [ ] **T7.3**: Verify picod binary exists in runtime image\n267:   - Purpose: Confirm binary copied from builder\n268:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n269:   - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-picod test -f /app/bin/picod`\n270: \n271: - [ ] **T7.4**: Verify workloadmanager runs as UID 1000\n272:   - Purpose: Confirm non-root security context\n273:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n274:   - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-workloadmanager id -u | grep \"1000\"`\n275: \n276: - [ ] **T7.5**: Verify router runs as UID 1000\n277:   - Purpose: Confirm non-root security context\n278:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile.router`\n279:   - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-router id -u | grep \"1000\"`\n280: \n281: - [ ] **T7.6**: Verify picod runs as root (UID 0)\n282:   - Purpose: Confirm root privileges for sandbox management\n283:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n284:   - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-picod id -u | grep \"0\"`\n285: \n286: - [ ] **T7.7**: Verify workloadmanager has no Go toolchain\n287:   - Purpose: Confirm minimal runtime (no build tools)\n288:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n289:   - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-workloadmanager which go 2>&1 | grep -v \"/usr\" || echo \"PASS\"`\n290: \n291: - [ ] **T7.8**: Verify workloadmanager has no Go source files\n292:   - Purpose: Confirm source not leaked to runtime\n293:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile`\n294:   - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-workloadmanager find /app -name \"*.go\" 2>/dev/null | wc -l | grep \"0\"`\n295: \n296: - [ ] **T7.9**: Verify picod has python3 installed\n297:   - Purpose: Confirm code execution dependency\n298:   - File: `docker/Dockerfile.picod`\n299:   - Verification: `docker run --rm agentcube-test-picod which python3`\n300: \n301: ### Phase 8: Makefile Integration Tests (ST-8)\n302: \n303: - [ ] **T8.1**: Run make docker-build successfully\n304:   - Purpose: Verify Makefile target works\n305:   - File: `Makefile`\n306:   - Verification: `make docker-build IMAGE_REPO=test VERSION=test`\n307: \n308: - [ ] **T8.2**: Run make docker-build-router successfully\n309:   - Purpose: Verify Makefile target works\n310:   - File: `Makefile`\n311:   - Verification: `make docker-build-router IMAGE_REPO=test VERSION=test`\n312: \n313: - [ ] **T8.3**: Run make docker-build-picod successfully\n314:   - Purpose: Verify Makefile target works\n315:   - File: `Makefile`\n316:   - Verification: `make docker-build-picod IMAGE_REPO=test VERSION=test`\n317: \n318: - [ ] **T8.4**: Run make docker-build-all successfully\n319:   - Purpose: Verify aggregate target builds all images\n320:   - File: `Makefile`\n321:   - Verification: `make docker-build-all IMAGE_REPO=test VERSION=test`\n322: \n323: ---\n324: \n325: ## Task Dependencies\n326: \n327: ```\n328: Phase 1 (WorkloadManager Dockerfile) ───────────────────────────────────────────\n329: T1.1 (builder FROM) ──┬── T1.2 (go mod download + cache)\n330:                       ├── T1.3 (COPY source + CGO_ENABLED)\n331:                       ├── T1.4 (go build + ldflags)\n332:                       ├── T1.5 (runtime FROM alpine)\n333:                       ├── T1.6 (apk packages)\n334:                       ├── T1.7 (adduser apiserver)\n335:                       ├── T1.8 (COPY --from=builder)\n336:                       ├── T1.9 (USER + EXPOSE)\n337:                       └── T1.10 (ENTRYPOINT)\n338: \n339: Phase 2 (Router Dockerfile) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n340: T2.1 (builder FROM) ──┬── T2.2 (go mod download + cache)\n341:                       ├── T2.3 (COPY client-go/)\n342:                       ├── T2.4 (CGO + go build)\n343:                       ├── T2.5 (runtime FROM alpine)\n344:                       ├── T2.6 (apk + adduser router)\n345:                       ├── T2.7 (COPY --from=builder + USER)\n346:                       └── T2.8 (EXPOSE + ENTRYPOINT)\n347: \n348: Phase 3 (PicoD Dockerfile) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n349: T3.1 (builder FROM golang) ──┬── T3.2 (go mod download)\n350:                              ├── T3.3 (CGO + go build)\n351:                              ├── T3.4 (runtime FROM ubuntu)\n352:                              ├── T3.5 (apt-get python3)\n353:                              ├── T3.6 (COPY --from=builder)\n354:                              └── T3.7 (EXPOSE + ENTRYPOINT)\n355: \n356: Phase 4 (Makefile Targets) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n357: T1.1-T1.10 ──┬── T4.1 (docker-build)\n358: T2.1-T2.8 ───┬── T4.2 (docker-build-router)\n359: T3.1-T3.7 ───┬── T4.3 (docker-build-picod)\n360:              ├── T4.4 (docker-build-all)\n361:              └── T4.5 (docker-buildx-push)\n362: \n363: Phase 5 (Syntax Validation) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n364: T1.1-T4.5 ──┬── T5.1-T5.9 (syntax checks)\n365: \n366: Phase 6 (Build Execution) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n367: T5.1-T5.9 ──┬── T6.1-T6.3 (build tests)\n368:             ├── T6.4-T6.6 (size verification)\n369: \n370: Phase 7 (Runtime Verification) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────\n371: T6.1-T6.6 ──┬── T7.1-T7.9 (runtime tests)\n372: \n373: Phase 8 (Makefile Integration) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────\n374: T4.1-T4.5 ──┬── T8.1-T8.4 (make target tests)\n375: ```\n376: \n377: ---\n378: \n379: ## Verification Commands\n380: \n381: | Task Phase | Verification Command |\n382: |------------|----------------------|\n383: | Phase 1 | `grep -c \"FROM\" docker/Dockerfile | grep \"2\"` |\n384: | Phase 2 | `grep -c \"FROM\" docker/Dockerfile.router | grep \"2\"` |\n385: | Phase 3 | `grep -c \"FROM\" docker/Dockerfile.picod | grep \"2\"` |\n386: | Phase 4 | `grep \"docker-build-all:\" Makefile` |\n387: | Phase 5 | `grep \"CGO_ENABLED=0\" docker/Dockerfile docker/Dockerfile.router docker/Dockerfile.picod` |\n388: | Phase 6 | `docker build -f docker/Dockerfile -t test-workloadmanager . && docker image inspect test-workloadmanager --format='{{.Size}}'` |\n389: | Phase 7 | `docker run --rm test-workloadmanager id -u | grep \"1000\"` |\n390: | Phase 8 | `make docker-build-all IMAGE_REPO=test VERSION=test` |\n391: \n392: ---\n393: \n394: ## Acceptance Criteria\n395: \n396: - [ ] WorkloadManager Dockerfile has 2-stage build structure\n397: - [ ] Router Dockerfile has 2-stage build structure\n398: - [ ] PicoD Dockerfile has 2-stage build structure\n399: - [ ] WorkloadManager uses golang:1.24-alpine builder + alpine:3.19 runtime\n400: - [ ] Router uses golang:1.24-alpine builder + alpine:3.19 runtime\n401: - [ ] PicoD uses golang:1.24 builder + ubuntu:24.04 runtime\n402: - [ ] WorkloadManager runs as UID 1000 (non-root)\n403: - [ ] Router runs as UID 1000 (non-root)\n404: - [ ] PicoD runs as root (UID 0)\n405: - [ ] All Dockerfiles have CGO_ENABLED=0\n406: - [ ] All Dockerfiles have ldflags=\"-w -s\" optimization\n407: - [ ] WorkloadManager/Router use BuildKit cache mounts for go mod/go build\n408: - [ ] Router Dockerfile includes client-go/ COPY\n409: - [ ] PicoD Dockerfile installs python3, python3-pip\n410: - [ ] WorkloadManager image size <50MB\n411: - [ ] Router image size <50MB\n412: - [ ] PicoD image size <100MB\n413: - [ ] Makefile has docker-build target\n414: - [ ] Makefile has docker-build-router target\n415: - [ ] Makefile has docker-build-picod target\n416: - [ ] Makefile has docker-build-all target\n417: - [ ] Makefile has docker-buildx-push targets for multi-arch\n418: - [ ] Runtime images have no Go toolchain\n419: - [ ] Runtime images have no Go source files\n420: - [ ] All images build successfully with make docker-build-all\n421: \n422: ---\n423: \n424: ## File Changes Summary\n425: \n426: | File | Action | Lines | Description |\n427: |------|--------|-------|-------------|\n428: | `docker/Dockerfile` | Create | 25 | WorkloadManager multi-stage build (builder → runtime) |\n429: | `docker/Dockerfile.router` | Create | 30 | Router multi-stage build (builder → runtime with client-go) |\n430: | `docker/Dockerfile.picod` | Create | 25 | PicoD multi-stage build (builder → Ubuntu runtime) |\n431: | `Makefile` | Modify | 35 | Add docker-build, docker-build-router, docker-build-picod, docker-build-all, docker-buildx-push targets |\n432: \n433: ---\n434: \n435: ## Implementation Notes\n436: \n437: ### Multi-Stage Build Pattern\n438: \n439: ```dockerfile\n440: # Stage 1: Builder\n441: FROM golang:1.24-alpine AS builder\n442: WORKDIR /app\n443: COPY go.mod go.sum ./\n444: RUN --mount=type=cache,target=/go/pkg/mod go mod download\n445: COPY . .\n446: ENV CGO_ENABLED=0\n447: RUN --mount=type=cache,target=/root/.cache/go-build \\\n448:     go build -ldflags=\"-w -s\" -o /app/bin/<binary> ./cmd/<module>\n449: \n450: # Stage 2: Runtime\n451: FROM alpine:3.19\n452: RUN apk add --no-cache ca-certificates tzdata\n453: RUN adduser -D -u 1000 <user>\n454: WORKDIR /app\n455: COPY --from=builder /app/bin/<binary> /app/bin/<binary>\n456: USER 1000\n457: EXPOSE 8080\n458: ENTRYPOINT [\" /app/bin/<binary>\"]\n459: ```\n460: \n461: ### BuildKit Cache Optimization\n462: \n463: | Cache Mount | Target | Purpose |\n464: |-------------|--------|---------|\n465: | `/go/pkg/mod` | Module cache | Persist module downloads across builds |\n466: | `/root/.cache/go-build` | Build cache | Cache compiled artifacts |\n467: \n468: ### Binary Size Optimization Flags\n469: \n470: | Flag | Effect |\n471: |------|--------|\n472: | `-w` | Strip DWARF debug information |\n473: | `-s` | Strip symbol table |\n474: | `CGO_ENABLED=0` | Static-like compilation |\n475: \n476: ### User Security Context\n477: \n478: | Image | User | Reason |\n479: |-------|------|--------|\n480: | WorkloadManager | UID 1000 | Non-root for security |\n481: | Router | UID 1000 | Non-root for security |\n482: | PicoD | root (UID 0) | Sandbox pod management requires elevated privileges |\n483: \n484: ---\n485: \n486: ## Implementation Timeline\n487: \n488: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n489: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n490: | Phase 1: WorkloadManager Dockerfile | T1.1-T1.10 | Pending | 0% |\n491: | Phase 2: Router Dockerfile | T2.1-T2.8 | Pending | 0% |\n492: | Phase 3: PicoD Dockerfile | T3.1-T3.7 | Pending | 0% |\n493: | Phase 4: Makefile Targets | T4.1-T4.5 | Pending | 0% |\n494: | Phase 5: Syntax Validation | T5.1-T5.9 | Pending | 0% |\n495: | Phase 6: Build Execution | T6.1-T6.6 | Pending | 0% |\n496: | Phase 7: Runtime Verification | T7.1-T7.9 | Pending | 0% |\n497: | Phase 8: Makefile Integration | T8.1-T8.4 | Pending | 0% |\n498: \n499: **Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/46 tasks)**\n500: \n501: ---\n502: \n503: ## References\n504: \n505: - Design: `changes/AR-032/design.md`\n506: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-032/delta-spec.md`\n507: - Proposal: `changes/AR-032/proposal.md`\n508: - Docker multi-stage builds: https://docs.docker.com/build/building/multi-stage/\n509: - BuildKit cache mounts: https://docs.docker.com/build/buildkit/#cache-mounts\n510: - Go cross-compilation: https://go.dev/doc/install/source#environment\n\n(End of file - total 510 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-032 — Dockerfile 多阶段构建 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-032 — Dockerfile 多阶段构建 (3 images) |\n| Module | `docker` |\n| Language | Dockerfile |\n| Size | S |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: WorkloadManager Dockerfile Foundation (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Create builder stage with golang:1.24-alpine base\n  - Purpose: Define builder stage for Go compilation","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260